#########################################
###      new design / refactor        ###
#########################################

            database
              ^ |
              | v
 inputs ->  control -> gui
(midi/osc)  (magi)  <- 
              | ^   
              v |
            model (resolume or other)

#########################################
###             the parts             ###
#########################################

- control aka MAGI -
	>the brains<
	gets input from
		inputs - midi or osc
		its own state (for example, when to loop)
		the gui
	interfaces with database to get/update info
	and passes said info to the model

- database -
	>the data<
	abstractions of clips
	collections to store clips
	methods to update or query database
	save/load 

- inputs -
	self-explanatory

- gui -
	whats happening right now
	what can be changed
	2 or 3 different guis
		1 - organizing collections
		2 - performance
		3 - recordings (nah)

- models -
	provide compatible api
	translate info coming in so that it can go out
		for example correcting clip commands
